"ogimage":"http://s3-media4.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/wAzv33sDeQugiR-oIJkQIQ/l.jpg",
"rating":"5.0",
"reviewcomment":"When you live abroad and are away from family, being able to conveniently place online orders for cakes and have them delivered on special occasions like Mother&#39;s Day, Father&#39;s Day, and birthdays is a godsend.<br><br>In comes, The Patissier. I&#39;ve ordered cakes from this place 3 times now for my in-laws in Singapore with a different cake flavor each time from their website- Pistachio Symphony, Jade Mirror and the Father&#39;s Day special Majesty. For each order, my in-laws commented on how delicious the cakes were. My MIL told me that when she first cut into the Jade Mirror, she had cut an additional slice for her husband but because it was so good, she ended up eating the second slice by herself. When they&#39;re happy, my husband and I are happy. <br><br>In addition to that, what impresses me most is the customer service of The Patissier. On two separate occasions, I needed the cake to be delivered before the earliest date that could be delivered as stated on the website when I was completing the online purchase. After I completed the order online, I emailed The Patissier to asked if it was possible to have the cake delivered before the earliest date given on their website. They gladly agreed to it with no additional fee. <br><br>I look forward to ordering more cakes from The Patissier!",
