"reviewcomment":"I was a bit skeptical about this place as it was a bit gimmicky. I had been to the outlet in California a few years ago and we got the whole sing and dancing shebang! We lined up for about 10 minutes which irked me a bit. But the person I was with promised me it was worth it. Perhaps the line wasn&#39;t such a bad thing because I couldn&#39;t decide what flavor I wanted. And I am not a indecisive person - it is just that ALL of the flavors looked amazing. <br><br>The vibe of the shop was super fun. Loud dance music and the servers were dancing, throwing up ice cream in the air and throwing it into cups. FUN! <br><br>I ordered the dark chocolate ice cream with oreos, peanut butter and peanuts. IT WAS ORGASMIC! It was so deliciously rich and creamy - almost chewy! I can see why this place has such a buzz and why people line up just to have some!!<br><br>A fun place to go with friends for a late night ice cream!",
