"reviewcomment":"I have always been a fan of baskin robbins. When i heard that they are reopening their outlet here in SIngapore. I was really excited about it. In the past, baskin robbins did not win many fans in Singapore due to their exotic colours of ice cream flavours. <br><br>But now, since its reopening, the crowd definitely show the acceptance of it.<br><br>My top list favourite ice cream is definitely cotton candy! It is a combination of colours of purple and pink. Love it to the max. The taste of it is really really unique. I have introduced this to many of my friends and they love it! Next flavour in rank is hokey pokey. Vanilla swirled with caramel ribbon.",
