"ogimage":"http://s3-media3.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/oUUx4Pbgmj3KnxpsCIRjAQ/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"Y&#39;know. I&#39;ve been coming to Sun Moulin since 2001, when the girl I was dating at the time introduced me to it.<br><br>Highschool loves come and go, but good bread is forever. 12 years later, and I&#39;m still eating the cheese and chocolate mochi, I&#39;m still in love with the Snow Chocolate bun, and there&#39;re still few other places I can find my croquette bun. The Snow Apple bun, which combines a crumbly cakey bread, custard, and apples, is another great item to try. I&#39;m also a fan of their curry bread, though it&#39;s really best fresh.<br><br>Sure, you have these shiny bakery chains springing up all over the place, but to me, none of them compare to Sun Moulin. You don&#39;t survive this long without being that good.",
