"reviewcomment":"J&#39;aime toutes les choses gâteau. And I mean seriously, love all things cake and by that measure Antoinette, you honey are my Asian cake princess.<br><br>The pastry execution here is top notch. Attention to detail at every piping turn. Excellent ingredients, quality butter and chocolate. You can not go wrong with a pot of tea and something from their case. Ever.<br><br>But despite what Marie-Antoinette says, one can not live off cake alone. Do not despair. Brunch at Antoinette is one of my required go tos every time I fly through Singapore. The eggs bennie are a personal favorite. The ambiance is fabulous, in a trendy ladies who lunch kind of way. Plush chairs. Ambient lighting. You just feel a little French noshing away on your savory crepe in here.",
