"ogimage":"http://s3-media2.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/IE9GvJ0lp4VT6xKkIsZIMA/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"This place has quite a few desserts that is worthy to try. One of it is the macaroons. I&#39;ve been in search for good macaroons ever since I step into Singapore. I love fruity taste macaroons so I tried strawberry, passion fruit and I forgot the other one. All of it are not that sweet which is good as I normally eat it in two bites without tea/coffee. The outside layer is crisp which is good. After eating the macaroons you will still have the flavour tangling on your tongue.<br><br>Another kind of pastry/ bread I would recommend is the mocha bread. The best is when you actually get it when it is fresh and bite straight into it. The top part is crispy and after biting, you will taste the mocha. I am not a fan of coffee but this is good and the price is reasonable.<br><br>This place is located at tower 3. Depending on where you park, you might need to walk more. Treat it exercise :) Enjoy. I hope that there will be more varieties of baked good soon!",
