"ogimage":"http://s3-media2.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/lg-9MM8cV9spWiyUmyZjPQ/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"I have to give major props to this ice cream shop. Competition for ice cream is fierce in the Upper Thomson area, with 4 or 5 ice cream/waffle shops all within a 5 minutes walk from each other. However, this place stands out so nicely because its 100% vegan, and they don&#39;t use processed/refined sugar, only a small amount unrefined cane sugar in their waffles and cane juice in their ice cream. I asked :) <br><br>Even their waffles are vegan, using no eggs or cows milk, and yet it was still delicious. I had 2 scoops of ice cream and a waffle, and by the end of finishing everything, I wasn&#39;t like super full or bloated, but I was definitely satisfied. Less guilt, and totally satisfied. That&#39;s a pretty good feeling coming out of an ice cream shop. <br><br>The service is also THE NICEST I have come across in Singapore, shocking to say since this is an ice cream shop. All smiles and super sweet. <br><br>They also serve free flow alkaline water with a high ph. I don&#39;t know any other ice cream shop, let alone restaurant that serves free flow alkaline water. Do you?!",
