"ogimage":"http://s3-media4.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/zIzDA7FCJH8sqhVGk_BbMg/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"The steam dumplings ($4 for 8pieces) and the Sour and Spicy soup ($3-smallest portion) here is really good! My aunt and I could not help downing the soup even though we were already stuffed, and we went home with bloated tummys. The soup was spicy and a really good appetizer, and had two fresh prawns in the thick, gooey soup along with bits of egg. My auntie even went so far as to return to the shop to compliment the auntie on her soup, while I made it a point to revisit this shop in future for their yummy dumplings as well. The skins of the dumplings are not thick and floury, and hence enjoyable. With soup in the dumpling and tender meat, these dumplings win the usual expensive dumplings we eat in shopping centres hands down. Opening hours: 11.30am-8pm.",
