"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"I LOVE this place! Possibly the healthiest option at Tanjong Pagar Market. <br><br>Thunder tea rice is a mix of rice (choice of brown or white), basil, peppermint leaves, leeks, peanuts, anchovies, pork floss, and among others, all paired with green tea sauce. The amount of water added to the sauce varies, but it ranges from a sauce like texture (think marinara) to soup (think broth). I prefer the former as I like to coat my mix rice with sauce to keep it from tasting like dry cardboard but avoiding the congee version as well. Sadly, this stall will be moving indefinitely to Chinatown Point once renovations start. <br><br>Come one, come all! You have until Feb. 28!",
